		<p>Hi Babs,</p>
<p>Yes. The dress is totally machine washable and dryable. For maximum wear, we suggest hand washing the dress in cold water, or machine-washing on the cold delicate cycle. Rather than machine drying, hang your dress to dry in the shade to preserve the dyes and prevent fading. Hope this helps!</p>

